text: Sir Henry Royce was born 27 March 1863 and died 22 April 1933. He made cars, and with Charles Stewart Rolls started the Rolls-Royce company. He was born in Alwalton, Huntingdonshire which is near Peterborough as the youngest child of five. Category:1863 births Category:1933 deaths Category:English businesspeople
title: Henry Royce
